content:
I’m Minghao, a senior undergraduate from UESTC. During my campus life, I’ve always been interested in the interdisciplinary of computer vision and artificial intelligence. More specifically, I am engaged in cross-domain object detection. Now I’m an undergraduate research assistant at the Data Intelligence Group(DIG) with the supervision of Prof. Lixin Duan and Wen Li.
This is for test!
